snippet.title: Introducing Cobblemon - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official Cobblemon trailer, a Pokemon mod for Minecraft Fabric/Forge 1.19.2

Cobblemon is a mod for Minecraft that introduces the world of Pokémon to Minecraft Java Edition. We have unique blocky Pokémon models, a transparent development team, and new in-game systems/mechanics.

Download Cobblemon here - https://cobblemon.com/
Join our Discord - https://discord.gg/cobblemon
View our latest upcoming features - https://twitter.com/cobblemonmod

Video Credits:
Models, textures and animations - The Cobblemon Team
Videographer/editor - https://www.youtube.com/@ProfessorKai/featured
